creator: Colbyno2
descriptionHtml:
Flowers are plants that everyone likes.
Flowers can make everyone happy for those who see it.
This application is a game about coloring flowers used with the help of numbers.

You can color the most beautiful flowers.
We have also updated to make this application more perfect than the previous version according to the user's request to be a beautiful flower.

There are hundreds of pictures of beautiful flowers that you can color as below:
rose
tulips
orchid
Gazania
alamanda
lotus
dahlia
lotus
sakura
jasmine
yellow rose
rainbow flower
flower photography
extraordinary flower
and many other types of interests and bonuses such as Mandala.

There are various colors that you can use to color, such as red, easy red, green, yellow, blue, purple, brown, gray, black and many favorite colors that you can find here

This game is suitable for kid and adults, can be colored from the easiest to the most difficult.

This game is good for free time and can also relieve stress.

The benefits of coloring with numbers are:
1. Develop Motor Skills.
2. As a Media of Expression.
3. Know the Color Difference.
4. Increasing Concentration.
5. Matching numbers and colors.
6. relieve stress
7. an exciting game

Rules:
1. Choose one of the flower images that you like in the library
2. Enlarge the image until the number appears
3. The color of the numbers matches the color you chose


The advantage:
+ Free coloring pictures
+ Simple tool
+ Add your own image from your mobile gallery to the pixel image created
+ You can share the results of coloring to all your friends.
+ pleasure and stress relief

So let's play together and have fun.
